{
  "stem": "27351.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew about how to survive now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the meantime, we spent two years, still two years to go in the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We worked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We starved.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- many of us, of course, were pulled out, and killed, and murdered, and sent out in transport.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] How to survive was the question.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, at the end, we started to hear the Po-- the, the Russian artillery, the Russian Katyusha.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It lasted a few days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was already January, January, 1945.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we started to hear the Katyushas.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And two weeks before it all ended, we were-- my mother and I lost our jobs, which meant we were in a group of people that was being collected to, to be-- to be sent.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, these lists were made by Jewish kapos.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And well, even if I know, I'm not talking about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She was a young woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was from the same school that we were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was one year older than my-- than my brother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was she was not bad, actually.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was asked to make a list, and she had to make a list.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she picked up a person who was older and a person who was younger, and sort of did not fit and may die anyway.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't-- Anyhow, at that point we were waiting for a transport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were just living for a few more days maybe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we lost our food rations, so we were starved.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we did something, I believe cleaning potatoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were frozen potatoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They put us there, so we ate the raw [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] skinned potato skins.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But then the 16th came, the 16th of January.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
